{"tid":1377594,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［香城Online]波子攻略毅進龍 一齊入嚟集思廣益下","createTime":"2019-07-28T14:11:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T14:52:56.000Z","uid":257625,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fb86851aec020bc3d7f246d487c7b955d241991d","tid":1377594,"uid":257625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:11:17.000Z","msg":"唔好意思啱啱開錯吹水台，再重新開一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n冇錯，波子冇可能一早放喺地下做陷阱<br />\n但係我哋調返轉嚟諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果我哋喺班毅進龍<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">沖緊過嚟嗰陣時</span></strong><br />\n我哋<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">先灑出去</span></strong>咁得唔得呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔使要好多，分散五六個人<br />\n大概攞住大概一支水樽份量嘅波子<br />\n再灑出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知呢個方法得唔得呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n集思廣益討伐毅進龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7a9c1c2ae4dfff1a51dad1f82794a40da3424b2","tid":1377594,"uid":257625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:12:39.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"1653b7d8d452e99c6b5a9b169558610a73da7f1d","tid":1377594,"uid":257625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:15:54.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"936c12d827295f920e6f0a27634b3a98cec5bd2a","tid":1377594,"uid":257625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T14:16:04.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"a4ee39bd6599550c453e79da078c3bc1f11421ac","tid":1377594,"uid":16326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTi